div.div:
• ABC = abstract base class
• This SVG is editable at diagrams.net (formerly known as draw.io), if you have write-access to the GitHub repo. Link:
https://app.diagrams.net/#Htfiers%2Fvoltage-to-wiring-sim%2Fmaster%2Fcode%2Fvoltage_to_wiring_sim%2Funits%2FUnits_class_diagram.svg
(Open this SVG with GitHub's "Raw" button if this link is not clickable).
• Note that manually editing the SVG's XML won't be reflected on diagrams.net.
This is because diagrams.net uses a custom data format for its diagrams, which it embeds as encoded binary data in exported SVGs. When opening an SVG file, it reads the data that it has previously embedded inside, and not the SVG's XML itself.
